commit.message: Add postcss

Release 0.4

- Improve detection of component sections
- Use narrowed indentation by default
- Allow indirect editing of all windows
- Add customizable indirect modes

Allow single quotes in top-level attributes

This highlights regions delimited by tags like `<template lang='pug'>`
Use vue-dedicated-modes in vue-mode-edit-all-indirect

Add dedicated mode mappings

Allows users to choose an alternative mode which is used in dedicated buffers
for any major mode usable in vue-mode.
Fix vue-modes customization type and docs

Fix off-by-one in indentation function

Now, the point immediately before the end of a submode is considered to be in
that submode.
Update README.md
